	'Gamingcalendar-20110803' => '* Insanely Twisted Shadow Planet
** SYSTEMS: XBLA
** DESCRIPTION: Insanely Twisted Shadow Planet is a side-scrolling adventure that is a fusion of art, classical animation, and captivating gameplay, created by artist, Michel Gagné, and game industry veteran, Joe Olson. It is developed by Shadow Planet Productions (Fuelcell Games and Gagne International). 
** IMAGE: http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110801180123/messaging/images/2/22/Shadowplanet.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://michelgagne.blogspot.com/

* Brink: Agents of Change
** SYSTEMS: Xbox 360, PS3, PC
** DESCRIPTION: Agents of Change is a DLC pack for Brink, that was announced on May 13, 2011 and set to be released on August 3, 2011. It will cost nothing on all platforms for the first two weeks, after which it will cost $9.99 USD. The pack contains additional content for the game, including Maps, Abilities, Attachments and clothing Archetypes, as well as raising the level cap from 20 to 24.
** IMAGE: http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110801181504/messaging/images/7/7f/Brink-Box-Art.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://brink.wikia.com/wiki/Brink_Wiki',
	'Gamingcalendar-20110809' => '* Sniper: Ghost Warrior|Extended Edition
** SYSTEMS: Xbox 360
** DESCRIPTION: When the democratic government of Isla Trueno is overthrown, an aggressive and hostile military command rises to power. A highly trained special ops unit is sent in to help the rebels accomplish objectives that only a sniper can handle. In addition to intense sniper missions, players will also take part in a variety of assault scenarios where their prowess with weapons will be a huge help to the undermanned rebels.
** IMAGE: http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110801182905/messaging/images/8/8b/SniperExtended.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://www.sniperghostwarrior.com
** PREORDER: http://www.gamestop.com/xbox-360/games/sniper-ghost-warrior-extended-edition/92571

*Spy Kids:|All the Time in the World
** SYSTEMS: Nintendo DS
** DESCRIPTION: Spy Kids: All the Time in the World is a platforming adventure based on the upcoming fourth movie in the Robert Rodriguez franchise. Stop the Timekeeper from taking over the world, using high-tech spy equipment and solving various puzzles.
** IMAGE: Spy Kids- All the Time in the World Poster.jpeg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://spykids.wikia.com/wiki/Spy_Kids_4:_All_the_Time_in_the_World',
	'Gamingcalendar-20110810' => '* Fruit Ninja Kinect
** SYSTEMS: Xbox 360
** DESCRIPTION: The self-described "messiest and most satisfying fruit game ever" comes to Microsoft\'s Xbox 360 with Kinect support. Wave your arms to slice, dice, and chop up various fruits before then can fall off the screen. But watch out for the bombs as hitting just one will end your game!
** IMAGE: http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110801184547/messaging/images/a/a0/Fruitninjakinect.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://www.fruitninja.com',
	'Gamingcalendar-20110816' => '*  No More Heroes:|Heroes\' Paradise
** SYSTEMS: PS3
** DESCRIPTION: Travis Touchdown touches down on the Playstation 3 in this port of the original Wii action hit. With Move support, updated graphics and other improvements, it should prove to be the definitive version of Suda51\'s off-beat masterpiece.
** IMAGE: http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110801185758/messaging/images/0/0d/Nomoreheroes.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://suda51.wikia.com/wiki/Suda51_Wiki
