* Age of Empires Online
** SYSTEMS: PC
** DESCRIPTION: Age of Empires Online – the next chapter in the best-selling Age of Empires PC game franchise – will be available worldwide August 16th, 2011 in retail stores and online at www.ageofempiresonline.com. With its launch, the game will feature two of the greatest ancient civilizations – the Greeks and Egyptians – and offer more than 40 hours of gameplay for free!
** IMAGE: http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110801190116/messaging/images/e/e1/Age-of-Empires-Online.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://ageofempiresonline.wikia.com/wiki/Age_of_Empires_Online_Wiki
** PREORDER: http://www.gamestop.com/pc/games/age-of-empires-online/91257

* Breath of Fire IV
** SYSTEMS: PSN, PSP
** DESCRIPTION: The classic Playstation RPG comes to the Playstation Network and the Playstation Portable to give gamers another chance to follow the adventures of the shape-shifting Ryu and his companions!
** IMAGE: http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110801191721/messaging/images/d/d3/Breath_of_fire.png|45px
** MOREINFO: http://bof.wikia.com',
	'Gamingcalendar-20110817' => '* From Dust
** SYSTEMS: PC
** DESCRIPTION: Shape the future of a dynamically changing planet by manipulating the very forces of nature in this ethereal title by acclaimed designer, Eric Chahi, creator of the classic Out Of This World.
** IMAGE: http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110801193260/messaging/images/2/22/From_dust.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://from-dust.ubi.com/from-dust/en-GB/home/',
	'Gamingcalendar-20110819' => '* Xenoblade Chronicles
** SYSTEMS: Wii
** DESCRIPTION: A new RPG from the makers of Xenosaga and Xenogears.Save the world from the fearsome robotic invaders!
** IMAGE: http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110421215438/xenoblade/images/1/17/XBBoxart.png|45px
** MOREINFO: http://xenoblade.wikia.com/wiki/Xenoblade_Chronicles',
	'Gamingcalendar-20110823' => '* Deus Ex:|Human Revolution
** SYSTEMS: Xbox 360, PS3, PC
** DESCRIPTION: The third and long-awaited chapter in the Deus Ex saga finally arrives. With open-ended gameplay and a twisty, suspenseful plot, Human Revolution has the potential to provide the same type of thrilling, innovative action that made the original a classic.
** IMAGE: http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110801200730/messaging/images/b/bc/Deus_Ex.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://deusex.wikia.com
** PREORDER: http://www.gamestop.com/pc/games/deus-ex-human-revolution-augmented-edition/88750#productDetails

* Street Fighter III: Third Strike|Online Edition
** SYSTEMS: PS3, Xbox 360
** DESCRIPTION: The classic fighting game returns in downloadable version for modern consoles. Which fighter will you choose?
** IMAGE: http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20080603175903/streetfighter/images/c/cd/Sf3logo.png|45px
** MOREINFO: http://streetfighter.wikia.com/wiki/Street_Fighter_III:_3rd_Strike

* Shin Megami Tensei:|Devil Survivor Overclocked
** SYSTEMS: Nintendo 3DS
** DESCRIPTION: Enhanced port of the original Devil Survivor. Stop the demon invasion of Tokyo with the help of your mysterious COMP device.
** IMAGE: http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20090517025833/megamitensei/images/e/e7/DevilSurvivorNABoxart.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://megamitensei.wikia.com/wiki/Shin_Megami_Tensei:_Devil_Survivor_-_Overclocked',
	'Gamingcalendar-20110830' => '* BloodRayne: Betrayal
** SYSTEMS: PS3
** DESCRIPTION: BloodRayne: Betrayal is a 2D side-scrolling spin-off  of the Bloodrayne series. Rayne, the sexy half-vampire, us recruited by the vampire hunting Brimstone Society to stop an evil vampire massacre.
** IMAGE: http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/egamia/images/f/f7/Bloodraynebetrayal.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://www.bloodraynebetrayal.com/

* Tropico 4
** SYSTEMS: PC, Xbox 360
** DESCRIPTION: Return to the role of a tropical island dictator in the fourth installment of the Tropico series, a city-building game with an over 20-mission campaign. New features include Facebook and Twitter integration.
** IMAGE: http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110630040927/tropico/images/7/7e/Tropico4_Box.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://tropico.wikia.com/wiki/Tropico_4

* The Sims Medieval:|Pirates & Nobles
** SYSTEMS: PC, Mac
** DESCRIPTION: The Sims Medieval Pirates & Nobles Adventure Pack introduces new quests, treasure hunting, and hundreds of new objects for your medieval kingdom! Your epic story starts when the Pirates of Aarbyville and the Nobles of Tredony arrive in your kingdom, followed quickly by sword fights, love affairs, grand adventures and mysteries. Go treasure hunting to uncover hidden objects. Embark on new quests to help your kingdom achieve a new ambition. Stylize your kingdom and Sims with new pirate and nobility themed objects and wardrobe. 
** IMAGE: http://images3.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110707231429/sims/images/2/2d/P%26N_Cover.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://sims.wikia.com/wiki/The_Sims_Medieval:_Pirates_and_Nobles',
	'Gamingcalendar-20110906' => '* Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine
** SYSTEMS: PC, PS3, Xbox 360
** DESCRIPTION: A third-person action-RPG set in the dystopian Warhammer 40,000 universe developed by Relic Entertainment and published by THQ. Players take the role of Captain Titus, a Space Marine of the Ultramarines Chapter. An Ork horde is launching an invasion on Graia, an Imperial Forge World – a planet-dedicated industry that manufactures vehicles and weaponry for the Imperium\'s soldiers.
** IMAGE: http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110608160806/spacemarine/images/e/e2/Space_Marine_cover_cropped.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://spacemarine.wikia.com',
	'Gamingcalendar-20110909' => '* Dead Island
** SYSTEMS: PC, PS3, Xbox 360
** DESCRIPTION: Dead Island is an open-ended game centered on survival and trying to find the protagonist\'s wife on a zombie-infested island. The game uses a first-person perspective; however, the game is not a first-person shooter due to a bigger emphasis on melee combat and ammunition conservation, rather than a shoot \'em up. Dead Island will run on Techland’s in house Chrome Engine, the same which powers Call of Juarez.
** IMAGE: http://images1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20110624113420/deadisland/images/7/79/Dead-Island_PS3_cover.jpg|45px
** MOREINFO: http://deadisland.wikia.com',
